條件<br />\n又嫌貴過隔離舖十幾廿蚊，又嫌隔離枱係咩人<br />\n煩過女人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你都幾撚柒煩我食野關你鬼事，仲有而家我有話唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 姐係你推介完我就一定要食，我話屎好食，你係咪跟住食呀傻鳩，你都幾撚專制wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> btw你一條友就係邊到食都無所謂啦死毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"825005778223deec4269e29fa2f25dec724e36e7","tid":471884,"uid":134220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T01:00:40.000Z","msg":"港島嘅大快活係好食啲"},{"pid":"e507d006272c1a3eede74f70d7abdf323b8a0af5","tid":471884,"uid":56147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T19:31:48.000Z","msg":"大快活<br />\n<br />\n一星期食兩至三次<br />\n<br />\n目測午市有2成人點咖哩"}]}